B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Wylde\" title=\"Coryanne Wylde\">Coryanne Wylde</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Howard Bullock</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> in service to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> during the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>. Howard, alongside his older brother Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Bullock\" title=\"Alyn Bullock\">Alyn</a>, served in the garrison at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> under the command of their father, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Merrell_Bullock\" title=\"Merrell Bullock\">Merrell Bullock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Bullock&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> was on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> during his regency, he spent every morning until midday in the castle yard training with sword, shield, and any other <a href=\"/index.php/Armament\" title=\"Armament\">armament</a>. The young king sparred with Ser Howard, his father <a href=\"/index.php/Merrell_Bullock\" title=\"Merrell Bullock\">Merrell</a>, his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Bullock\" title=\"Alyn Bullock\">Alyn</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Elyas_Scales\" title=\"Elyas Scales\">Elyas Scales</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/50_AC\" title=\"50 AC\">50&#160;AC</a>, Howard fled Dragonstone with Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Coryanne_Wylde\" title=\"Coryanne Wylde\">Coryanne Wylde</a>, taking most of his wife's <a href=\"/index.php/Jewelry\" title=\"Jewelry\">jewelry</a> with them. A fishing boat took them to <a href=\"/index.php/Driftmark\" title=\"Driftmark\">Driftmark</a>, where they took ship for <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> and then made their way to the <a href=\"/index.php/Disputed_Lands\" title=\"Disputed Lands\">Disputed Lands</a>, where Howard joined the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Company_(sellsword_company)\" title=\"Free Company (sellsword company)\">Free Company</a>. He died in <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_53_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">53&#160;AC</a> after falling from his <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a> after a night of <a href=\"/index.php/Alcoholic_beverages\" title=\"Alcoholic beverages\">drinking</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Bullock&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Merrell_Bullock\" title=\"Merrell Bullock\">Merrell</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em